.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
A C++23 console application to generate a yearly calendar\&. 

This program accepts a four-digit year and prints a formatted calendar for that year to the standard output\&. It handles leap year logic, calculates the starting day of the week automatically, and formats the output using \fRstd::print\fP and ANSI color codes\&.
.IP "\(bu" 2
\fBNote\fP
.RS 4
This program requires a C++23 compliant compiler due to the usage of \fR<print>\fP and \fRstd::format\fP\&. 
.RE
.PP

.PP

